title: Ahmed Atiq Anwer wins NA-113 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan Muslim League Nawaz (PML-N) Candidate Ahmed Atiq Anwer has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-113 Sheikhupura-I by securing 1,19,407 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Independent candidate Rahat Aman Ullah Bhatti, who bagged 90,872 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 49.88 percent.
